AttributeList.Text: 20 - Move stopper for wedge according to the parameters
25 - Wait before support to work position - handshake with other instances
40 - Start hydraulic cylinder to switching position - approach speed and force
50 - Switching position - wait for handshake with other instances
60 - Start hydraulic cylinder to H2 position - final speed and force
100 - return - wait for handshake with other instances
200 - Move all cylinders to basic - evaluate result
